{"tid":1550361,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【數據分折，重溫 ！】想自殺？想重刷首抽？入黎睇睇先！","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T02:53:00.000Z","uid":27814,"like":116,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ebe6213b7c975e30aeed3d4a0d83a8e8954f9b","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鑑於大量自殺潮，想同大家重溫，此post發起人為會員#59224 林曉音</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近連登負能量比較多<br />\n出現咗好多留言不停鼓勵各位自殺，重新投胎搵過戶好人家<br />\n更加有巴打不幸身先士卒<br />\n不過口講無憑，自殺到底可唔可以成功改變命運呢？<br />\n我地冇辦法從已經過身嘅巴打攞料<br />\n不過我地可以運用統計學，估算各位投胎轉世成功機會有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先，雖然人類分開唔同種族同民族，但佢地都係同一個物種<br />\n所以我地假設一個人死咗，下世仍然身為人類嘅話，都有機會投胎去世界各國<br />\n透過分析各國出生人口數目，就可以搵出投胎去某個國家嘅機會啦<br />\n雖然投胎去某個窮國唔代表下世一定係窮人，投胎去發達國家都唔代表下世一定飛黃騰達<br />\n但係一個人身處咩國家，大概代表到呢個人嘅生活水平同幸福程度<br />\n更重要嘅係，透過數據分析，各位可以搵到下世到底會去咗邊度<br />\n睇完之後先再衡量下值唔值得死都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦，事不且遲，我地直接睇統計結果啦<br />\n下面所有數據都係由The World Factbook拎到，原文係英文。因為樓主趕住出post，排名太後嘅國家就懶得譯返漢字名，大家明就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215202_334d980100e9817ef1b53d2e71a3235a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215202_334d980100e9817ef1b53d2e71a3235a.jpg&h=42ae0b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215203_78ce91c3a1ee49784e8e02e9dd642c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215203_78ce91c3a1ee49784e8e02e9dd642c26.jpg&h=551ddca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215203_73f00cdac2696b15e67b7a26a5b397fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215203_73f00cdac2696b15e67b7a26a5b397fa.jpg&h=4a71e406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215204_fe728157a5a025ecf15cf39cccdf3260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215204_fe728157a5a025ecf15cf39cccdf3260.jpg&h=67ae9a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/215204_ed5d0742f2cfc6aa2604689c9cf8fed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F215204_ed5d0742f2cfc6aa2604689c9cf8fed7.jpg&h=161545a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntoo long didn't read？我黎同大家解釋一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前十名國家合計嘅投胎機率有54.25%，即係你下世有超過一半機會投胎係呢十個國家，而呢啲國家大多數唔係窮，就係貧富懸殊或者冇自由。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一名係印度，各位有17.92%機會做印度人</span><br />\n可以瘋狂食咖哩同去恆河沖屎水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更重要嘅係印度種姓制度遺害極深，萬一你出身「賤民」種姓就慘過食十舊屎<br />\n再者印度女性地位非常低，投胎做咗印度妹就自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第二名就係偉大嘅中國，投胎機會達12.48%</span><br />\n詳細情況就唔多講啦，總之即使你地死咗，都仲有八份之一嘅機會共享中國人榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前十名國家當中只有美國投得過，但得3%投胎機會<br />\n搏唔搏得過就自己考慮下啦<br />\n不過你唔係投胎去到美國就一勞永逸，你估美國冇窮人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿，我地眼光放遠啲，睇到頭50個國家咁多。<br />\n佢地合計嘅投胎機率有86.1%，姐係你下世好有可能會係五十個國家嘅其中之一出世。<br />\n撇開前十名唔計，係頭50個國家入面，算得上發達國家嘅只有日本、法國、英國同德國<br />\n佢地加埋美國，總投胎機率都只有5.41%<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姐係你下世會有86.1% - 5.41% = 80.69%機會去咗落後國家，咁就一世</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以大家好唔好砍掉重練呢？<br />\n相信大家諗到呢步，人生路中一定好唔好彩，受咗好多苦。<br />\n嘅然係咁，點解你地仲想自殺呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地黎到今時今日都咁唔好彩，憑咩相信你投胎就會突然黎運，投去好國家呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n總而言之，投胎轉世涉及風險，下世有多過八成機會慘過而家，人生更可變得毫無價值。投胎未必一定有賺，反而可能會招致損失。<br />\n自殺前請三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9b55de75c5ce2ca95f01c4f4f5ed0f57f4d9eb","tid":1550361,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9ec6514ed94d03fff33e7c5464bb2c82dfa903d","tid":1550361,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>2019年香港自殺資料統計</ins></strong><br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=9b2bd774\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=3807d762\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=76144d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>"},{"pid":"4b984aa0327d918fb070918408118a7fd2ba1b33","tid":1550361,"uid":156509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"推，有數據有分析有正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c725983562d8cf7852e2bc24f2f5155bd9df4eea","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"be90f8eaeb3a32f69db9bfa64a2ea39455701bf5","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1acf2b54f12ac9c3f1e2da30548fe36878344056","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"0dda520071c7986f457d05da7b10da4665c6f48e","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:41.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"da402db25de22d44650c06634cf6dd8aa09c1ca9","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"beff8a275bb5d14b8db914d2c1ad43ca4ffbd99c","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7513ccc2b7ff76b74780fda021043786f1bdeeda","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f66b5f50588eb68c2c74462d02399578bd516004","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8b72f499000f2dbe4e79cecd651ddbd3b57959ad","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"baef25f70082b18be605209f576b72397f27f79b","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"54a992d29c5301a9c2328010549df0782d58db4c","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"傳說中既10連<br />\n竟然破左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af46236e8b7b22d7e37d42e20c96df6dedd52cb7","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"黎多個10連<br />\n救得一個得一個"},{"pid":"fde82a405d2ab4cb377f1e073d9fcdb68f302a59","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"06a425d406b6bab63c3634230ed303323ce9a85d","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"333a7f10c09e4d572066806a850510efd400b3c3","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"dfb645e50e7f251d819188a279339f8896fb031b","tid":1550361,"uid":304267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb302365200c3f0f374ab778c06b56362b71c954","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"977f8e5177607228fc4758323c1eebcb93db04dd","tid":1550361,"uid":304726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家手足唔好放棄，苦盡甘來呀！比啲信念！！"},{"pid":"1f416008b4af58c05b5f60446eed595d31a6b95f","tid":1550361,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":